<h2 id="start-monitoring-in-seconds">Start Monitoring in Seconds</h2>
<p id="p3">Add any website or RSS feed with a tap. Send notifications from any script or web app with a simple webhook. Your device does all the work &ndash; complete privacy, zero dependencies.</p>
